snippet.textDisplay:
For all those who still don't know why people are talking about SBS and Wendy the problem is that when Redvelvet were rehearsing one of the staff told Wendy to use the stairs 😒 which were led by a dark tunnel Wendy fell 2.5 meters because there were no stairs and no markings or anything which would guide her and it was dark so she couldn't see and she fell she got serious injuries like she broke her pelvis, cracked her cheek bone and fractured her hip all because of SBS also they didn't apologize which made the fans angry and they demanded a apology letter and when they apologized it was more of a apology to the fans and other audience not to Redvelvet or Wendy also it made it seem like it was Wendy's fault when it wasn't and so due to Wendy's injuries they won't be having any promotions or anything which is not even anything I care about now because thank god she's only injured she could've died and this could effect her career. Just pray for Wendy's speedy recovery 💕
#GetWellSoonWendy
